  "notes": "Union Cave 1F connects Route 32 (north) to Route 33 (south), making it a mandatory transit dungeon early in the game. The cave is accessible without any HMs or badges. Two staircases at (5,19) and (3,33) descend to B1F. Five trainers are present: Hiker Daniel (x3,y6), Hiker Russell (x11,y8), Pokemaniac Larry (x4,y21), Firebreather Bill (x14,y19), Firebreather Ray (x15,y27). Four item balls: X Attack (x4,y2), Potion (x4,y17), Great Ball (x17,y21), Awakening (x12,y33). Sandshrew appears in morning/day but NOT at night (replaced by Wooper). Pokemaniac Larry's post-battle dialogue hints at the Friday Lapras event in B2F. Tileset $09 confirmed in attributes.asm. Source: maps/UnionCave1F.asm."
